{
  "stem": "22047.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 17.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not that I recall.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] When I was growing up, well, particularly in Santa Barbara, most of the-- of the fellas I palled around with were Italian, like Vince [ITALIAN], I didn't mention, and Dick [ITALIAN].",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were-- they were Italian.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't recall any Jewish families.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm sure there were some, but in those days, I didn't know Italian from Chinese, hardly.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I was color blind.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Everybody was just another person, and if he was my friend, he was my friend.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I didn't much care what his nationality was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Same way.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- I don't think I ever-- in fact, I'm not now, am I-- do I have really any prejudices, except for bad actors, but there's bad actors in any nationality.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I don't recall any particular [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] thoughts one way or another about a person's background, or their nationality, or anything.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We have a-- I have a very good Jewish friend in our church.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, this is rather unique.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She's-- she's Jewish and-- and has Jewish faith, but she attends our church, Methodist Church, and she's very active in it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She's a delightful person, sings in the choir.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And our minister, former minister, was black.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Just a beautiful, beautiful person, he and his wife.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he was elevated recently to a District Superintendent in San Francisco.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So he's got 56 churches under his direction now.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I think I'm very non-prejudiced.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm sure they did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because among the teachers that they were associated with, I'm sure there were some Jewish folks.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But again, I didn't attach any significance to-- to them as Jewish, or Italian, or Greek, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
